  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1070">
<l>karappavark kiyāṅkoḷikkuṅ kollō virappārkkuc</l>
<l>collāṭap pōo muyir</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying "No" to a beggar takes away his life. (but as that very word will kill the refuser) where then would the latter's life hide itself ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
